{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sami is a 2D platformer fantasy adventure that combines narrative storytelling, meditative puzzles, and exploration to create an immersive experience centered on emotional well-being and mindfulness. Players will embark on a journey alongside Sunu, as he navigates different worlds, each rich with its own challenges and symbolism. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/cinematic2_SAMI.gif?t=1737651684\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sami is not just about overcoming obstacles\u2014it's about reflection, transformation, and self-discovery.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/The_World_of_SAMI_english.png?t=1737651684\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as Sunu, an ancestral oniric being in search of spiritual evolution. He travels through surreal environments where light and shadow constantly vie for dominance, reflecting his internal struggles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/GifSunuMundo.gif?t=1737651684\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The narrative is designed to provoke deep thoughts and personal reflection, encouraging players to question their own emotions and inner conflicts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/The_Guardian_Gifts_english.png?t=1737651684\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout his journey, Sunu must aid lost souls, guiding them back to the right path while also grappling with his own doubts and fears. You get to use a set of special abilities, like the Ohm, to collect yout inner peace to transform everything around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/samigif1-3.gif?t=1737651684\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/Gameplay_SAMI.gif?t=1737651684\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/Phases_Levels_english.png?t=1737651684\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game levels are inspired by the different phases of mental health, divided in 6 magical worlds with unique visual aesthetics. Explore each level while transforming misguided souls, invoke guardians powers and boosters, and solve meditative puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/Levels_english.png?t=1737651684\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/phases_sami-1.gif?t=1737651684\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/extras/Logo_SAMI.png?t=1737651684\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737651684","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/page.bg.jpg?t=1737651684","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3358740/c8d1fa40a1baf342ffa3ae8a68137adb7